    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Video Game Developer - Providing a Single Example\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a video game developer by adding a single example to help guide the AI's dialogue.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI to generate a conversation by including **a brief example** of a hero-sidekick exchange.\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, noticing how the AI uses the example to shape tone, style, or plot.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Write a very short dialogue between a superhero and their sidekick where the sidekick is lovable but foolish. For example:\r\n>\r\n> Hero: \"I told you to stay in the jet!\"\r\n>\r\n> Sidekick: \"And miss this explosion? Never.\"\r\n:::",
